{% capture rock_stepper_elevate_content %}
  <details class="rs-elevate__details" open>
    <summary class="rs-elevate__summary">
      <span class="rs-elevate__summary-text">
        <span class="rs-elevate__title">Elevate Your Home Workouts with the 3D 2-in-1 Rock Stepper</span>
        <span class="rs-elevate__meta">
          <span class="rs-elevate__label">Learn more</span>
          <span class="rs-elevate__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" focusable="false" role="presentation">
              <path d="M3.5 6.25 8 10.75l4.5-4.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </span>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <div class="details-content rs-elevate__content">
      <p class="rs-elevate__lede">Unlike limited mini steppers, our rock stepper delivers a dynamic training system. The dual-mode design allows you to switch freely between cardio and strength training.</p>

      <ul class="rs-elevate__list">
        <li><strong>Gliding mode:</strong> Achieve a steady, low-impact cardio rhythm that mimics cross-country skiing for warm-ups or sustained calorie burn.</li>
        <li><strong>Stepping mode:</strong> Focus on deeper lower-body engagement to target and tone your legs, glutes, and hips for building strength and endurance.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Moreover, the unique 3D dynamic rocking motion delivers a smoother, more natural stride. This 3D movement actively engages your core, glutes, and stabilizer muscles for a more efficient stepper workout.</p>

      <h3 class="rs-elevate__heading">Smart Full-Body Mini Stepper for Home Use</h3>
      <p>Forget cords and complicated settings. This mini stair stepper is powered by your own body weight, providing natural, adjustable resistance. The built-in counter tracks every step, keeping you motivated and accountable. The included bands attach securely, allowing you to simultaneously sculpt your arms, shoulders, and back. Its space-saving design makes it perfect for apartments, home offices, or small gyms. You can store it in a closet or under a desk with ease.</p>

      <h3 class="rs-elevate__heading">Ideal For Dynamic, Space-Smart Fitness Lovers</h3>
      <p>This versatile rocking stepper is designed for users who want maximum results from minimal equipment. It is the perfect match for:</p>

      <ul class="rs-elevate__list">
        <li><strong>Apartment &amp; small-space dwellers:</strong> Who need a compact stair stepper that delivers a full-body workout without taking up much space.</li>
        <li><strong>Sedentary workers:</strong> Seeking a quick, effective exercise break to improve posture and combat sedentary hours.</li>
        <li><strong>Workout variety seekers:</strong> Those who want to switch between cardio gliding and strength-focused stepping.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>At Merach, we engineer fitness solutions that fit seamlessly into your world. We combine versatile dual-mode training, space-saving portability, and effective full-body resistance into a single, user-friendly device for unparalleled home workouts. Making consistent, effective fitness achievable for everyone, everywhere.</p>

      <button
        type="button"
        class="rs-elevate__collapse"
        aria-label="Show less"
        onclick="const details=this.closest('details');if(details){details.open=false;const summary=details.querySelector('summary');if(summary){summary.focus();}}"
      >
        <span>Show less</span>
        <span class="rs-elevate__arrow rs-elevate__arrow--up" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" focusable="false" role="presentation">
            <path d="M3.5 6.25 8 10.75l4.5-4.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </details>
{% endcapture %}

<div class="rs-elevate">
  {% render 'accordion-custom-component', children: rock_stepper_elevate_content %}
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .rs-elevate {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .rs-elevate__details {
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb), 0.12);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb), 0.04) 0%,
      rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb), 0.02) 100%
    );
  }

  .rs-elevate__summary {
    display: block;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .rs-elevate__summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .rs-elevate__summary::marker {
    content: '';
  }

  .rs-elevate__summary-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .rs-elevate__title {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.7rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .rs-elevate__meta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    width: fit-content;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb), 0.72);
  }

  .rs-elevate__details[open] .rs-elevate__meta {
    display: none;
  }

  .rs-elevate__arrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 1rem;
    height: 1rem;
    transition: transform var(--animation-speed-slow) var(--animation-easing);
  }

  .rs-elevate__arrow svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .rs-elevate__arrow--up {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .rs-elevate__content {
    padding: 0 1.75rem 1.75rem;
  }

  .rs-elevate__content p,
  .rs-elevate__content li {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb), 0.78);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .rs-elevate__content p + p,
  .rs-elevate__content p + ul,
  .rs-elevate__content p + h3,
  .rs-elevate__content ul + p,
  .rs-elevate__content ul + h3,
  .rs-elevate__content h3 + p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .rs-elevate__lede {
    font-size: 1.02rem;
  }

  .rs-elevate__heading {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .rs-elevate__list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .rs-elevate__list li + li {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .rs-elevate__collapse {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding: 0;
    border: 0;
    background: transparent;
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb), 0.72);
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .rs-elevate__summary {
      padding: 1.25rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .rs-elevate__content {
      padding: 0 1.25rem 1.25rem;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}
